1.1 Introduction
================

SUNDIALS CVODE integration for maxima-numerics
(https://github.com/cmsd2/maxima-numerics).  Provides production-grade
ODE solving via the SUNDIALS
(https://computing.llnl.gov/projects/sundials) library from Lawrence
Livermore National Laboratory.

Features:

   • *CVODE solver* -- variable-order Adams (non-stiff) and BDF (stiff)
     methods
   • *Event detection* -- zero-crossing rootfinding during integration
   • *Two calling modes* -- expression mode (symbolic RHS) and function
     mode (callable RHS), matching the ‘np_odeint’ conventions

