1.1.1 Prerequisites
-------------------

SUNDIALS v6.0+ must be installed on your system:

macOS:   brew install sundials
Debian:  sudo apt install libsundials-dev
Fedora:  sudo dnf install sundials-devel
Windows: vcpkg install sundials


